quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  4,142,"Bato ya bilongi mibale bazali koluka kokosa Allah, kasi (Allah) azali kobalola kokosa na bango. Mpe soki batelemi mpona kosambela, bakotelema na bolembu, bazali koluka bato bamona bango, mpe bazalaka koluka kokanisa Allah mingi te"
  4,143,"Bazali mbilinga mbilinga, bazali epai ya bandimi te epai ya bapagano mpe te, moto oyo Allah apengwisi ye okozongisa ye na nzela te"
  4,144,Eh bino bandimi! Botika bandimi te mpona kozua bapagano baninga na bino. Bolingi kotiela Allah elembo polele likolo na bino
  4,145,"Bato ya bilongi mibale ya sôló, bakozala na nsé ya moto ya lifelo. Mpe bakozuaka mpona bango mosungi te"
  4,146,"Longola sé baye batubeli mpe babongisi, sima bakangami na Allah, mpe babongisi lingomba na bango mpona Allah; bango wana nde bazali na bandimi elongo mpe Allah akopesa bandimi lifuta ya monene"
  4,147,Allah akopesa bino etumbu te soki bopesi ye botondi mpe bondimi naye. Mpe Allah atonda botondi azali moyebi
  4,148,"Allah alingaka te basakola maloba ya mabe, sé soki na moto oyo abubami Allah azali oyo ayokaka atonda boyebi"
  4,149,"Soki bobimisi bolamu polele to bobombi yango, to mpe bolimbisi mabe, ya sôló Allah atonda nguya atonda bolimbisi"
  4,150,"Ya sôló, baye bazali kompengwa na Allah na batindami naye, mpe balingaka kokabola Allah na batindami naye, mpe balobaka ete: Tondimi na ndambu mpe tompengwi na ndambu, mpe balukaka na yango nzela ya kobimela"
  4,151,Bango wana nde bazali bapagano ya sôló; mpe tosili kobongisela bapagano etumbu ya makasi
  4,152,"Mpe ba oyo bandimi na Allah na batindami naye, mpe bakaboli kati na batindami naye te, bango wana nde bakozua lifuta na bango. Mpe Allah azali molimbisi atonda ngolu"